---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---
<Layout
  title="Future Projects | Accessibility Research Lab | Western Washington University">

	<div class="page-content">
		<div class="region-wrapper">
			<h1 class="page-title">Future Projects</h1>
			<div class="layout--twocol-section layout--twocol-section--50-50">
				<div class="layout__region layout__region--first">
					<div class="blue-bg standard-padding standard-margin--bottom full-height">
						<h2 class="text-align-center">Accessible Drafting</h2>
						<p>3D is for more than just movies. We plan to partner with the engineering department to utilize 3D printers as input devices for computer-aided drafting programs. We’ll use haptics (technology designed around the sense of touch) and audio queues for boundary alerts so that a blind drafter can create drawings with precision. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="layout__region layout__region--second">
					<div class="blue-bg standard-padding standard-margin--bottom full-height">
						<h2 class="text-align-center">Fully Accessible Maps</h2>
						<p>We at ARL would like to create a fully accessible digital map of Western’s campus so that it can be navigated with greater ease and confidence. This project promotes student mobility safety and success. </p>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="vertical-space--2x"></div>
			<div class="layout--twocol-section layout--twocol-section--50-50">
				<div class="layout__region layout__region--first">
					<div class="blue-bg standard-padding standard-margin--bottom full-height">
						<h2 class="text-align-center">Fully Accessible Virtual Tour</h2>
						<p>We plan to create a fully accessible virtual tour so that all Western departments and divisions can promote the features that our campus has to offer</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="layout__region layout__region--second">
					<div class="blue-bg standard-padding standard-margin--bottom full-height">
						<h2 class="text-align-center">Accessible XR</h2>
						<p>We want to create accessible XR for all humans.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="vertical-space--2x"></div>
		</div> <!-- end region-wrapper -->
	</div> <!-- end page-content -->

</layout>